Sec. 14.058. POSTING OF STORAGE RATES OR TARIFFS. (a) A
public grain warehouse licensed under this chapter shall post a copy
of all storage rates and tariffs charged by the warehouse operator at
the main warehouse office and at each warehouse facility operating
under the license.
(b) The warehouse operator shall post any change to the posted
storage rates or tariffs not later than the third day before the day
on which the change is to take effect.
(c) Department inspectors shall check compliance with this
section during inspections of a public grain warehouse under this
chapter.
Renumbered from Sec. 14.036 and amended by Acts 2001, 77th Leg., ch.
1124, Sec. 1, eff. Sept. 1, 2001.

